{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892547496,"sessionID":"ses_284909cb8ffeOsd4or1kukodLL","part":{"id":"prt_d7b71c36c001ubcGg9jZSdxMOI","messageID":"msg_d7b71ba2d001OLuXwECFRFE7Xj","sessionID":"ses_284909cb8ffeOsd4or1kukodLL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7b351fef66954c81bea0bd8f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Scope\n11: \n12: This delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n17: \n18: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n19: \n20: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: 成功创建 AgentRuntime Sandbox\n23: \n24: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\"AgentRuntime\", Name, Namespace 已填）\n25:   AND DynamicClient 已配置\n26:   AND AgentRuntime CR 模板存在于目标 namespace\n27:   AND Store 可写\n28:   AND Reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce 可正常返回 channel\n29: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context)` 被调用\n30: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\n31:   AND 响应体包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n32:   AND AgentRuntime CR 已创建到集群\n33:   AND Sandbox 信息已持久化到 Store\n34:   AND 响应中 EntryPoints 包含从 PodIP + TargetPorts 构建的 endpoint 列表\n35: \n36: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 校验失败\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: 请求体 JSON 解析失败\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** 请求体为非法 JSON\n41: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n42: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n43:   AND 响应包含 JSON 解析错误信息\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 请求体校验失败 — 缺少必填字段\n46: \n47: - **GIVEN** CreateSandboxRequest 缺少 Name 或 Namespace\n48: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n49: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n50:   AND 响应包含校验失败信息\n51:   AND 未创建任何 CR\n52:   AND Store 未被写入\n53: \n54: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 模板不存在\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 模板未找到\n57: \n58: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest\n59:   AND 目标 namespace 中不存在匹配的 AgentRuntime CR 模板\n60: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n61: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n62:   AND 响应体包含 \"agent runtime template not found\" 类错误\n63:   AND 未创建 Sandbox CR\n64: \n65: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox CR 创建失败自动回滚\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 创建失败触发回滚\n68: \n69: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板存在\n70:   AND 动态客户端在创建 Sandbox CR 时返回错误（如网络不可达）\n71: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n72: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n73:   AND 已创建的 AgentRuntime CR 被 `rollbackCR` 清理\n74:   AND Store 中无残留记录\n75: \n76: ### Requirement: buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR 注入元数据\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: CR 构建包含所有必需 label 和 annotation\n79: \n80: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板 CR\n81:   AND sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace 已生成\n82: - **WHEN** `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 被调用\n83: - **THEN** 返回 unstructured CR 对象\n84:   AND `metadata.labels` 包含 `app.kubernetes.io/managed-by`, `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`, `runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name`, `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name`\n85:   AND `metadata.annotations` 包含 `last-activity-time`\n86:   AND spec 从模板正确复制\n87: \n88: ### Requirement: generateSessionID 生成 UUID\n89: \n90: #### Scenario: 生成唯一 session ID\n91: \n92: - **GIVEN** 无\n93: - **WHEN** `generateSessionID()` 被调用\n94: - **THEN** 返回非空字符串\n95:   AND 多次调用返回值不同\n96:   AND 格式符合 UUID 规范\n97: \n98: ### Requirement: generateSandboxName 命名规则\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: sandbox 名称格式\n101: \n102: - **GIVEN** `workloadName = \"my-workload\"`\n103: - **WHEN** `generateSandboxName(workloadName)` 被调用\n104: - **THEN** 返回 `\"my-workload-<随机后缀>\"`\n105:   AND 总长度 ≤ 63 字符（Kubernetes name 限制）\n106:   AND 后缀为小写字母+数字\n107: \n108: ### Requirement: getPortsOrDefaults 端口回退\n109: \n110: #### Scenario: 空端口列表使用默认值\n111: \n112: - **GIVEN** 空的 TargetPort 列表\n113: - **WHEN** `getPortsOrDefaults(ports)` 被调用\n114: - **THEN** 返回包含默认端口 8080 的列表\n115:   AND protocol 为 TCP\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: 非空端口列表原样返回\n118: \n119: - **GIVEN** `ports = [{port: 8080, protocol: \"TCP\"}]`\n120: - **WHEN** `getPortsOrDefaults(ports)` 被调用\n121: - **THEN** 原样返回输入列表\n122: \n123: ### Requirement: buildEntryPoints 构建端点列表\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: 从 PodIP 和端口构建 EntryPoints\n126: \n127: - **GIVEN** `podIP = \"10.0.0.5\"`\n128:   AND `ports = [{port: 8080, protocol: \"TCP\", path: \"/\"}, {port: 8081, protocol: \"HTTP\", path: \"/api\"}]`\n129: - **WHEN** `buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)` 被调用\n130: - **THEN** 返回 EntryPoint 列表\n131:   AND 每个 EntryPoints 的 Endpoint 格式为 `\"http://10.0.0.5:<port>\"`\n132:   AND Path 和 Protocol 正确映射\n133: \n134: ### Requirement: injectPicodAuthEnv 注入认证环境变量\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: 认证启用时注入 Secret 引用\n137: \n138: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n139:   AND unstructured CR 对象\n140:   AND namespace 中存在 `\"picod-router-identity\"` Secret，包含 `\"public.pem\"` 数据\n141: - **WHEN** `injectPicodAuthEnv` 被调用\n142: - **THEN** CR 的 `spec.template.spec.containers[0].env` 中注入 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量\n143:   AND 值引用 Secret\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: 认证禁用时不修改 CR\n146: \n147: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = false`\n148: - **WHEN** `injectPicodAuthEnv` 被调用\n149: - **THEN** 不修改 CR 的 env 字段\n150: \n151: ### Requirement: resolvePodIP 从 Sandbox CR 解析 Pod IP\n152: \n153: #### Scenario: Pod 已分配 IP\n154: \n155: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已创建且 `annotations[\"agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name\"]` 存在\n156:   AND 对应 Pod 已运行且 `status.podIP` 不为空\n157: - **WHEN** `resolvePodIP` 被调用\n158: - **THEN** 返回 Pod 的 IP 地址\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: Pod 尚未绑定\n161: \n162: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 存在但未绑定 Pod（无 `sandbox-pod-name` annotation）\n163: - **WHEN** `resolvePodIP` 被调用\n164: - **THEN** 返回空字符串和错误\n165: \n166: ### Requirement: rollbackCR 清理已创建的 CR\n167: \n168: #### Scenario: 成功删除 CR\n169: \n170: - **GIVEN** 一个已创建的 CR（GVR, namespace, name 已知）\n171: - **WHEN** `rollbackCR` 被调用\n172: - **THEN** CR 被从集群中删除\n173: \n174: #### Scenario: CR 已不存在时不报错\n175: \n176: - **GIVEN** CR 已被删除\n177: - **WHEN** `rollbackCR` 被调用\n178: - **THEN** 不返回错误（IsNotFound 被忽略）\n179: \n180: ---\n181: \n182: ## R-2: Sandbox 创建 — CodeInterpreter\n183: \n184: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`, `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR`\n185: \n186: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 成功路径\n187: \n188: #### Scenario: 成功创建 CodeInterpreter Sandbox\n189: \n190: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\"CodeInterpreter\"）\n191:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 模板存在\n192:   AND 所有依赖（DynamicClient, Store, Reconciler）可用\n193: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n194: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\n195:   AND 响应包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n196:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 已创建\n197:   AND Sandbox 信息已持久化到 Store\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 模板不存在\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 模板未找到\n202: \n203: - **GIVEN** 目标 namespace 中不存在 CodeInterpreter CR 模板\n204: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n205: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n206:   AND 错误信息指明模板未找到\n207: \n208: ### Requirement: CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox 创建失败自动回滚\n209: \n210: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 创建失败触发回滚\n211: \n212: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 模板存在\n213:   AND 创建 Sandbox CR 时 DynamicClient 返回错误\n214: - **WHEN** `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 被调用\n215: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n216:   AND 已创建的 CodeInterpreter CR 被回滚清理\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR 构建 CR\n219: \n220: #### Scenario: CR 构建包含所有必需元数据\n221: \n222: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 模板 CR\n223:   AND sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace, ports 已提供\n224: - **WHEN** `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` 被调用\n225: - **THEN** 返回 unstructured CR 对象和 podName\n226:   AND `metadata.labels` 包含所有必需 label（ManagedBy, SessionID, WorkloadName, SandboxName）\n227:   AND spec 从模板正确复制\n228:   AND 返回的 podName 非空\n229: \n230: ---\n231: \n232: ## R-3: Sandbox 创建 — 认证与动态客户端\n233: \n234: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `getDynamicClient`; `handler/models.go` — `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate`\n235: \n236: ### Requirement: getDynamicClient 认证模式\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: 认证启用且 token 有效\n239: \n240: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n241:   AND 请求头中包含有效的 Authorization Bearer token\n242:   AND TokenCache.GetOrCreateUserK8sClient 返回有效的 dynamic client\n243: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n244: - **THEN** 返回 dynamic.Interface\n245:   AND 无错误\n246: \n247: #### Scenario: 认证启用但 token 缺失\n248: \n249: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = true`\n250:   AND 请求头中不包含 Authorization 头\n251: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n252: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 401\n253:   AND 错误信息指明缺少认证 token\n254: \n255: #### Scenario: 认证模式禁用\n256: \n257: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth = false`\n258: - **WHEN** `getDynamicClient` 被调用\n259: - **THEN** 返回包级别默认的 DynamicClient\n260:   AND 无错误\n261: \n262: ### Requirement: CreateSandboxRequest.Validate\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: Kind 为空\n265: \n266: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n267: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n268: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"kind is required\"`\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Name 为空\n271: \n272: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n273: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n274: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"name is required\"`\n275: \n276: #### Scenario: Namespace 为空\n277: \n278: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"\"}`\n279: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n280: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"namespace is required\"`\n281: \n282: #### Scenario: 所有字段有效\n283: \n284: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n285: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n286: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n287: \n288: ---\n289: \n290: ## R-4: Reconciler — AgentRuntime 调和\n291: \n292: **Scope:** `reconciler/agentruntime.go` — `reconcileAgentRuntime`, `mapConditionToStatus`, `isNotFoundError`\n293: \n294: ### Requirement: reconcileAgentRuntime 调和逻辑\n295: \n296: #### Scenario: 新建 AgentRuntime（Pending 状态）\n297: \n298: - **GIVEN** key 格式为 `\"namespace/name\"`\n299:   AND AgentRuntime CR 存在于 informer lister\n300:   AND CR 状态为 Pending（无 Ready condition）\n301:   AND Store 中无对应 session 记录\n302: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n303: - **THEN** 返回 nil（无错误）\n304:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileTotal` 被调用，result=success\n305: \n306: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 变为 Ready\n307: \n308: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}`\n309:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录\n310: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n311: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Running\n312:   AND 返回 nil\n313: \n314: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 终止\n315: \n316: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"False\", reason: \"Terminated\"}`\n317:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录\n318: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n319: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Terminated\n320:   AND 返回 nil\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: CR 已被删除\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** key 对应的 AgentRuntime CR 已被删除\n325: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n326: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除对应 session\n327:   AND 返回 nil（不视为错误）\n328: \n329: #### Scenario: key 格式无效\n330: \n331: - **GIVEN** `key = \"invalid-key-no-slash\"`\n332: - **WHEN** `reconcileAgentRuntime(key)` 被调用\n333: - **THEN** 返回错误，包含 `\"unexpected key format\"`\n334:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileErrors` 被调用\n335: \n336: ### Requirement: mapConditionToStatus 条件映射\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: Ready=True 映射为 running\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}]`\n341: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n342: - **THEN** 返回 `\"running\"`\n343: \n344: #### Scenario: Ready=False + Terminated 映射为 terminated\n345: \n346: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"False\", reason: \"Terminated\"}]`\n347: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n348: - **THEN** 返回 `\"terminated\"`\n349: \n350: #### Scenario: 空条件列表映射为 pending\n351: \n352: - **GIVEN** `conditions = []`\n353: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n354: - **THEN** 返回 `\"pending\"`\n355: \n356: #### Scenario: Ready=Unknown 映射为 pending\n357: \n358: - **GIVEN** `conditions = [{type: \"Ready\", status: \"Unknown\"}]`\n359: - **WHEN** `mapConditionToStatus(conditions)` 被调用\n360: - **THEN** 返回 `\"pending\"`\n361: \n362: ### Requirement: isNotFoundError 识别\n363: \n364: #### Scenario: NotFound 错误返回 true\n365: \n366: - **GIVEN** `err = errors.NewNotFound(schema.GroupResource{}, \"name\")`\n367: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n368: - **THEN** 返回 true\n369: \n370: #### Scenario: 非 NotFound 错误返回 false\n371: \n372: - **GIVEN** `err = errors.NewInternalError(fmt.Errorf(\"internal\"))`\n373: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n374: - **THEN** 返回 false\n375: \n376: #### Scenario: nil 错误返回 false\n377: \n378: - **GIVEN** `err = nil`\n379: - **WHEN** `isNotFoundError(err)` 被调用\n380: - **THEN** 返回 false\n381: \n382: ---\n383: \n384: ## R-5: Reconciler — CodeInterpreter 调和\n385: \n386: **Scope:** `reconciler/codeinterpreter.go` — `reconcileCodeInterpreter`\n387: \n388: ### Requirement: reconcileCodeInterpreter 调和逻辑\n389: \n390: #### Scenario: 新建 CodeInterpreter（Pending 状态）\n391: \n392: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n393:   AND CodeInterpreter CR 存在于 lister\n394:   AND CR 状态为 Pending\n395: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n396: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n397:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileTotal(resourceTypeCodeInterpreter, resultSuccess)` 被调用\n398: \n399: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 变为 Ready\n400: \n401: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter CR 的 `status.conditions` 包含 `{type: \"Ready\", status: \"True\"}`\n402: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n403: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 Status 为 Running\n404:   AND 返回 nil\n405: \n406: #### Scenario: CR 已被删除\n407: \n408: - **GIVEN** key 对应的 CodeInterpreter CR 已被删除\n409: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n410: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除对应 session\n411:   AND 返回 nil\n412: \n413: #### Scenario: key 格式无效\n414: \n415: - **GIVEN** `key = \"no-slash\"`\n416: - **WHEN** `reconcileCodeInterpreter(key)` 被调用\n417: - **THEN** 返回错误\n418:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncReconcileErrors` 被调用\n419: \n420: ---\n421: \n422: ## R-6: Reconciler — Pod 调和\n423: \n424: **Scope:** `reconciler/pod.go` — `reconcilePod`, `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo`, `extractPort`\n425: \n426: ### Requirement: reconcilePod 调和逻辑\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: Pod 已就绪并分配 IP\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/pod-name\"`\n431:   AND Pod 的 `status.podIP` 不为空\n432:   AND Store 中存在对应 session 记录（通过 label 匹配）\n433: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n434: - **THEN** 更新 Store 中 SandboxInfo 的 PodIP\n435:   AND 更新 EntryPoints 列表（基于 PodIP + 端口）\n436:   AND 返回 nil\n437: \n438: #### Scenario: Pod 未分配 IP\n439: \n440: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 `status.podIP` 为空\n441: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n442: - **THEN** 返回 nil（等待下次调和）\n443:   AND 不更新 Store\n444: \n445: #### Scenario: 非管理的 Pod（无 session label）\n446: \n447: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 labels 中不包含 `LabelSessionID`\n448: - **WHEN** `reconcilePod(key)` 被调用\n449: - **THEN** 返回 nil（忽略非管理 Pod）\n450: \n451: ### Requirement: buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo\n452: \n453: #### Scenario: 使用 PodIP 更新 EntryPoints\n454: \n455: - **GIVEN** SandboxInfo 包含 EntryPoints 模板\n456:   AND `podIP = \"10.0.0.5\"`\n457: - **WHEN** `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo(info, podIP)` 被调用\n458: - **THEN** 返回 EntryPoint 列表，Endpoint 中使用 podIP 替换原有占位符\n459: \n460: ### Requirement: extractPort 提取端口\n461: \n462: #### Scenario: 从 URL 提取端口\n463: \n464: - **GIVEN** `endpoint = \"http://10.0.0.5:8080/api\"`\n465: - **WHEN** `extractPort(endpoint)` 被调用\n466: - **THEN** 返回 `\"8080\"`\n467: \n468: #### Scenario: 无端口时使用默认值\n469: \n470: - **GIVEN** `endpoint = \"10.0.0.5\"`（无端口）\n471: - **WHEN** `extractPort(endpoint)` 被调用\n472: - **THEN** 返回 `\"80\"`（默认值）\n473: \n474: ---\n475: \n476: ## R-7: Reconciler — 事件处理器\n477: \n478: **Scope:** `reconciler/event_handlers.go` — 所有 `on*Add`/`on*Update`/`on*Delete` 处理器\n479: \n480: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime 事件入队\n481: \n482: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 新增事件\n483: \n484: - **GIVEN** 一个新增的 AgentRuntime 对象\n485: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdd(obj)` 被调用\n486: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用，key 格式为 `\"namespace/name\"`\n487: \n488: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 状态变化触发更新\n489: \n490: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 的 `status.conditions` 发生变化\n491: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n492: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n493: \n494: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 非状态变化不触发更新\n495: \n496: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 仅 `metadata.resourceVersion` 变化，status 不变\n497: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n498: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add` 不被调用\n499: \n500: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 删除事件\n501: \n502: - **GIVEN** 一个被删除的 AgentRuntime 对象\n503: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeDelete(obj)` 被调用\n504: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n505: \n506: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter 事件入队\n507: \n508: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Add/Update/Delete 事件\n509: \n510: - **GIVEN** 对应的 CodeInterpreter 事件（Add/Update/Delete）\n511: - **WHEN** 对应的 `onCodeInterpreter*` 处理器被调用\n512: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(key)` 被调用\n513: \n514: ### Requirement: Pod 事件入队\n515: \n516: #### Scenario: 带 session label 的 Pod 新增\n517: \n518: - **GIVEN** 新增的 Pod 包含 `LabelSessionID` label\n519: - **WHEN** `onPodAdd(obj)` 被调用\n520: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n521: \n522: #### Scenario: 不带 session label 的 Pod 被忽略\n523: \n524: - **GIVEN** 新增的 Pod 不包含 `LabelSessionID` label\n525: - **WHEN** `onPodAdd(obj)` 被调用\n526: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add` 不被调用\n527: \n528: #### Scenario: Pod IP 变化触发更新\n529: \n530: - **GIVEN** Pod 的 `status.podIP` 从空变为非空\n531: - **WHEN** `onPodUpdate(oldObj, newObj)` 被调用\n532: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n533: \n534: #### Scenario: Pod 删除事件\n535: \n536: - **GIVEN** 一个被删除的 Pod\n537: - **WHEN** `onPodDelete(obj)` 被调用\n538: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(podKey)` 被调用\n539: \n540: ---\n541: \n542: ## R-8: Reconciler — 工作队列与同步\n543: \n544: **Scope:** `reconciler/sync.go`, `reconciler/reconciler.go` — `syncHandler`, `processNextWorkItem`, `runWorker`, `determineResourceType`, `Enqueue`, `Run`, `WatchSandboxOnce`\n545: \n546: ### Requirement: syncHandler 同步处理\n547: \n548: #### Scenario: 成功处理并 Forget\n549: \n550: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"` 对应存在的 AgentRuntime\n551:   AND 调和逻辑无错误\n552: - **WHEN** `syncHandler(key)` 被调用\n553: - **THEN** 返回 nil\n554:   AND `workqueue.Forget(key)` 被调用\n555: \n556: #### Scenario: 处理失败触发重试\n557: \n558: - **GIVEN** key 对应的调和逻辑返回错误\n559: - **WHEN** `syncHandler(key)` 被调用\n560: - **THEN** 错误被返回\n561:   AND `workqueue.AddRateLimited(key)` 被调用\n562: \n563: ### Requirement: determineResourceType 资源类型判断\n564: \n565: #### Scenario: key 对应 AgentRuntime\n566: \n567: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n568:   AND AgentRuntime lister 中存在该 key\n569: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n570: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypeAgentRuntime`\n571: \n572: #### Scenario: key 对应 CodeInterpreter\n573: \n574: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/name\"`\n575:   AND AgentRuntime lister 中不存在，但 CodeInterpreter lister 中存在\n576: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n577: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypeCodeInterpreter`\n578: \n579: #### Scenario: key 对应 Pod\n580: \n581: - **GIVEN** `key = \"namespace/pod-name\"`\n582:   AND AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter lister 中均不存在\n583: - **WHEN** `determineResourceType(key)` 被调用\n584: - **THEN** 返回 `resourceTypePod`\n585: \n586: ### Requirement: Enqueue 入队\n587: \n588: #### Scenario: 按 namespace/name 入队\n589: \n590: - **GIVEN** `namespace = \"default\"`, `name = \"my-sandbox\"`\n591: - **WHEN** `Enqueue(namespace, name)` 被调用\n592: - **THEN** `workqueue.Add(\"default/my-sandbox\")` 被调用\n593: \n594: ### Requirement: Run 启动与关闭\n595: \n596: #### Scenario: 启动指定数量的 worker\n597: \n598: - **GIVEN** `workers = 2`\n599:   AND cache sync 成功\n600: - **WHEN** `Run(stopCh)` 被调用\n601: - **THEN** 启动 2 个 worker goroutine\n602:   AND `metricsRecorder.SetWorkqueueDepth` 被周期性调用\n603:   AND 当 stopCh 关闭时，所有 worker 退出\n604: \n605: #### Scenario: cache sync 超时\n606: \n607: - **GIVEN** informer cache 无法在 30s 内同步\n608: - **WHEN** `Run(stopCh)` 被调用\n609: - **THEN** 记录错误日志\n610:   AND 函数返回，不启动 worker\n611: \n612: ### Requirement: WatchSandboxOnce 单次等待\n613: \n614: #### Scenario: 等待 Sandbox 就绪\n615: \n616: - **GIVEN** namespace/name 对应的 Sandbox 尚未就绪\n617: - **WHEN** `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name)` 被调用\n618: - **THEN** 返回一个 channel\n619:   AND 当 reconciler 处理该 key 后，channel 收到 SandboxStatus\n620:   AND channel 在收到消息后关闭\n621: \n622: #### Scenario: 重复调用相同 key\n623: \n624: - **GIVEN** 已有一个活跃的 `WatchSandboxOnce` 调用在等待\n625: - **WHEN** 再次调用 `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name)`（相同 key）\n626: - **THEN** 返回错误（或复用已有 channel）\n627: \n628: ### Requirement: processNextWorkItem 出队处理\n629: \n630: #### Scenario: 队列中有 item\n631: \n632: - **GIVEN** workqueue 中有一个 item\n633: - **WHEN** `processNextWorkItem()` 被调用\n634: - **THEN** 返回 true\n635:   AND item 被处理\n636:   AND `syncHandler` 被调用\n637: \n638: #### Scenario: 队列为空\n639: \n640: - **GIVEN** workqueue 为空\n641: - **WHEN** `processNextWorkItem()` 被调用\n642: - **THEN** 返回 false\n643: \n644: ---\n645: \n646: ## R-9: Lifecycle — 空闲超时与注解解析\n647: \n648: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` — `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations`, `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR`, `calculateTimeToIdle`\n649: \n650: ### Requirement: parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations 注解解析\n651: \n652: #### Scenario: 有效注解值\n653: \n654: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"30m\"}`\n655: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n656: - **THEN** 返回 `30m`\n657: \n658: #### Scenario: 无效注解值回退默认值\n659: \n660: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"invalid\"}`\n661: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n662: - **THEN** 返回默认值 `15m`\n663: \n664: #### Scenario: 无注解使用默认值\n665: \n666: - **GIVEN** `annotations = {}`\n667: - **WHEN** `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations, 15m)` 被调用\n668: - **THEN** 返回默认值 `15m`\n669: \n670: ### Requirement: extractIdleTimeoutFromCR 从 CR 提取\n671: \n672: #### Scenario: CR 注解包含空闲超时\n673: \n674: - **GIVEN** CR 的 `metadata.annotations` 包含 `\"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\": \"20m\"`\n675: - **WHEN** `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR(cr, 15m)` 被调用\n676: - **THEN** 返回 `20m`\n677: \n678: ### Requirement: calculateTimeToIdle 计算剩余空闲时间\n679: \n680: #### Scenario: 未空闲\n681: \n682: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt = now - 5m`\n683:   AND `idleTimeout = 15m`\n684: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n685: - **THEN** 返回 `*time.Duration = 10m`（剩余空闲时间）\n686: \n687: #### Scenario: 已空闲超时\n688: \n689: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt = now - 20m`\n690:   AND `idleTimeout = 15m`\n691: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n692: - **THEN** 返回 nil（已超时）\n693: \n694: #### Scenario: 无活动时间视为已空闲\n695: \n696: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.LastActivityAt` 为零值\n697: - **WHEN** `calculateTimeToIdle(info, now)` 被调用\n698: - **THEN** 返回 nil（视为已空闲）\n699: \n700: ---\n701: \n702: ## R-10: Lifecycle — GC 清理\n703: \n704: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` — `cleanupOrphanCRs`, `cleanupGhostEntries`, `runGCCycle`\n705: \n706: ### Requirement: cleanupOrphanCRs 孤立 CR 清理\n707: \n708: #### Scenario: 发现并删除孤立 CR\n709: \n710: - **GIVEN** 集群中存在 AgentRuntime CR，其 label 中的 sessionID 在 Store 中无对应记录\n711: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n712: - **THEN** 删除孤立 CR\n713:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncGCCleanupTotal(GRCleanupReasonOrphanCR)` 被调用\n714:   AND 返回删除数量 > 0\n715: \n716: #### Scenario: 无孤立 CR\n717: \n718: - **GIVEN** 所有 CR 的 sessionID 都能在 Store 中找到对应记录\n719: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n720: - **THEN** 返回 0\n721:   AND 无删除操作\n722: \n723: #### Scenario: 达到扫描上限\n724: \n725: - **GIVEN** 孤立 CR 数量 > `MaxOrphanScanLimit` (100)\n726: - **WHEN** `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx)` 被调用\n727: - **THEN** 最多删除 100 个 CR\n728:   AND 记录警告日志\n729: \n730: ### Requirement: cleanupGhostEntries 幽灵条目清理\n731: \n732: #### Scenario: 发现并清理幽灵条目\n733: \n734: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session 记录，但对应的 CR（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）已不存在于集群\n735: - **WHEN** `cleanupGhostEntries(ctx)` 被调用\n736: - **THEN** 从 Store 中删除幽灵条目\n737:   AND `metricsRecorder.IncGCCleanupTotal(GRCleanupReasonGhostEntry)` 被调用\n738:   AND 返回清理数量\n739: \n740: #### Scenario: 无幽灵条目\n741: \n742: - **GIVEN** 所有 Store 记录对应的 CR 都存在于集群\n743: - **WHEN** `cleanupGhostEntries(ctx)` 被调用\n744: - **THEN** 返回 0\n745: \n746: ### Requirement: runGCCycle 完整 GC 周期\n747: \n748: #### Scenario: 执行完整 GC 周期\n749: \n750: - **GIVEN** 存在过期 Sandbox、空闲 Sandbox、孤立 CR、幽灵条目\n751: - **WHEN** `runGCCycle(ctx)` 被调用\n752: - **THEN** 依次执行 `cleanupExpiredSandboxes`, `cleanupOrphanCRs`, `cleanupGhostEntries`\n753:   AND `metricsRecorder.ObserveGCCycleDuration` 记录总耗时\n754:   AND 每种清理原因的 `IncGCCleanupTotal` 被正确调用\n755: \n756: ---\n757: \n758: ## R-11: Sandbox 创建 Handler — 依赖注入与构造\n759: \n760: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `NewSandboxCreateHandler`, `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps`\n761: \n762: ### Requirement: NewSandboxCreateHandler 构造\n763: \n764: #### Scenario: 有效依赖构造 handler\n765: \n766: - **GIVEN** 有效的 `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps`（所有字段非 nil）\n767: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps)` 被调用\n768: - **THEN** 返回非 nil 的 `SandboxCreateHandler`\n769:   AND handler 内部字段与 deps 一致\n770: \n771: ---\n772: \n773: ## R-12: RandString 工具函数\n774: \n775: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `RandString`\n776: \n777: ### Requirement: RandString 随机字符串生成\n778: \n779: #### Scenario: 指定长度\n780: \n781: - **GIVEN** `n = 10`\n782: - **WHEN** `RandString(10)` 被调用\n783: - **THEN** 返回长度为 10 的字符串\n784:   AND 仅包含小写字母和数字\n785: \n786: #### Scenario: 随机性\n787: \n788: - **GIVEN** 无\n789: - **WHEN** 连续调用 `RandString(10)` 两次\n790: - **THEN** 两次返回值不同的概率 > 99.9%\n791: \n792: #### Scenario: 零长度\n793: \n794: - **GIVEN** `n = 0`\n795: - **WHEN** `RandString(0)` 被调用\n796: - **THEN** 返回空字符串\n797: \n798: #### Scenario: 最小长度\n799: \n800: - **GIVEN** `n = 1`\n801: - **WHEN** `RandString(1)` 被调用\n802: - **THEN** 返回长度为 1 的字符串\n803: \n804: ---\n805: \n806: ## File Structure\n807: \n808: | Path | Role |\n809: |------|------|\n810: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | **NEW** — Sandbox 创建流程测试 |\n811: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models_test.go` | **NEW** — CreateSandboxRequest.Validate 测试 |\n812: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | **NEW** — AgentRuntime 调和测试 |\n813: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | **NEW** — CodeInterpreter 调和测试 |\n814: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod_test.go` | **NEW** — Pod 调和测试 |\n815: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | **NEW** — 事件处理器测试 |\n816: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` | **NEW** — 工作队列与同步测试 |\n817: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | **NEW** — Reconciler 生命周期测试 |\n818: \n819: ## Dependencies\n820: \n821: - `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert`, `github.com/stretchr/testify/require` — 断言库（已有）\n822: - `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` — 动态客户端 mock（已有）\n823: - `k8s.io/client-go/testing` — reactor 注册\n824: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` — scheme 注册\n825: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/fake` — 伪造 clientset\n826: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` — HTTP handler 测试（已有）\n\n(End of file - total 826 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Scope\n\nThis delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n\n---\n\n## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n\n**Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n\n### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775892547485,"end":1775892547493}}}}
